WEBVTT

00:01.719 --> 00:05.689
Adjectives are words that describe someone or something

00:10.083 --> 00:11.889
This bear is big.

00:17.995 --> 00:20.424
This bear is small.

00:26.164 --> 00:29.244
She is very tall.

00:35.976 --> 00:38.662
The penguins are short.

00:46.063 --> 00:48.889
This young boy can dance.

00:53.374 --> 00:55.598
This old man can dance too!

01:04.247 --> 01:06.352
They are rich.

01:13.454 --> 01:16.918
She is poor.

01:26.142 --> 01:27.303
He is happy.

01:35.119 --> 01:37.111
She is very sad.

